-- Concrete resource for the news feed
one sig NewsFeed extends Resource {}


----------------------------------------------------------------------
-- Whole-model verification summary
----------------------------------------------------------------------

-- Summary 1: Model enforces initiator authorization (SAFETY-1) and resource access control (SAFETY-2).
-- Summary 2: Structural well-formedness requires at least one channel, one resource, pre != post, and authenticated channel.
-- Summary 3: Test scenarios capture feed display with no friends, one friend, new friend post, and friend deletion.
-- Summary 4: Non-functional invariants constrain channel count (2-3) and resource count (1-5).
-- Assumption 1: Permission lattice equates stronger with superset; unused in assertions.
-- Assumption 2: Friendship model is represented implicitly via accessible field of NewsFeed resource.
-- Assumption 3: Post deletion is modeled by removing actor from accessible set.
-- Open issue 1: Edge case assertion ec_safe_1 uses Friendship_API (Interface) in set of Resources; remains vacuously true.
-- Open issue 2: Post-time ordering is not explicitly modeled; sorting assumed via implicit state ordering.
-- Open issue 3: No explicit mapping from friends to posts beyond shared accessible set.


